tip.text: Nice place and great food and drinks. Would definitively come back for the lamb shank, lamb steak and the meat pie, NZ style. Wines are mostly from NZ. Yes the owner is a Kiwi
Banana cake and the scones are nice and moist, great with coffee.  Should have named the place not Levain, but Devine
